===[[Noun]]===
#(grammatical terminology) a verbal [[mood]] expressing an order.  In English, the imperative is the same as the "you" form of the verb - ''Get it'', ''Do it'', ''Go over there'', ''Say what you like''.
#an essential action, a must: something which is imperative.
:''Visiting Berlin is an imperative.''

